title: an example defining all three kinds of Thing
pid: b3f2aede-5b0c-492c-b55c-e876bc257ffc
body: |2-
  define

  object           sub entity;
  resource         sub object;
  file             sub resource,
     owns path,
     owns size-kb,
     plays object-ownership:object;

  path             sub attribute, value string;
  size-kb          sub attribute, value long;

  object-ownership sub relation,
     relates object;
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
